overview:
Matt is a web programmer and developer who specializes in PHP, MySQL and Javascript applications, has owned a few businesses, and is now getting into the web startup arena.

With over 11 years of development experience, Matt has worked on hundreds of websites for both agencies and while being self employed. He also has some web hosting knowledge gained from owning a hosting business, and is familiar with marketing through a marketing business he also owned.

These days Matt is more focused on building his own web-startup FBiframes.com, which is already becoming a success, and is looking forward to being in the field for a long time.
